title: Indonesia Consumer Spending
description: Consumer Spending in Indonesia decreased to 1545455.50 IDR Billion in the third quarter of 2022 from 1550035 IDR Billion in the second quarter of 2022. Consumer Spending in Indonesia averaged 1260676.32 IDR Billion from 2010 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 1550035 IDR Billion in the second quarter of 2022 and a record low of 926097.50 IDR Billion in the first quarter of 2010. This page provides - Indonesia Consumer Spending - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Statistics Indonesia
